<taxonomicName id="B0E4EA48AF07D1FB61046515B696C060" class="Insecta" family="Sialidae" genus="Leptosialis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Leptosialis africana" order="Megaloptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="29" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="africana">Leptosialis africana</taxonomicName>
Esben-Petersen, female, holotype 2 same, male 3 
<taxonomicName id="C9E03A59BE6AF0EB2F7EC487682FE3D0" class="Insecta" family="Sialidae" genus="Leptosialis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Leptosialis necopinata" order="Megaloptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="29" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="necopinata">Leptosialis necopinata</taxonomicName>
sp. n. male, holotype 4 same, female. Scale bars = 5.0 mm
</paragraph>
